21
00:04:34,366 --> 00:04:35,951
<i>You guys set to launch?</i>

22
00:04:36,285 --> 00:04:39,705
Yeah, Brock. Launching Dunkin now.
Go, Charlie.

23
00:04:47,797 --> 00:04:49,632
- <i>All right, tether out.</i>
- Tether out.

24
00:04:50,508 --> 00:04:53,511
