we're dropping down along the hull.</i>

25
00:04:56,138 --> 00:04:58,182
Yeah, roger that.
Okay, drop down and go

26
00:04:58,224 --> 00:05:00,142
into the first-class gangway door.

27
00:05:00,476 --> 00:05:02,254
I want you guys working the "D" deck,

28
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:04,688
<i>reception area
