29
00:05:05,481 --> 00:05:06,482
<font color="#878787">TECHNICIAN</font>: <i>Copy that.</i>

30
00:05:12,696 --> 00:05:13,823
<i>Tether out...</i>

31
00:05:13,848 --> 00:05:16,745
<i>- Okay, now left. Now left. Left, left.
